OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FToday marks 10 years since Didcot
OL,8,FPower station collapsed killing four
OL,9,Fmen.
OL,11,FThe workers were preparing the site
OL,12,Ffor demolition - when part of the
OL,13,Fboiler house collapsed on 23 February
OL,14,F2016.
OL,16,FIt took six months for the bodies of
OL,17,FJohn Shaw, Ken Cresswell, Michael
OL,18,FCollings and Christopher Huxtable to
OL,19,Fbe recovered.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
