OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FAn investigation involving Thames
OL,8,FValley Police and the Health and
OL,9,FSafety Executive is expected to be
OL,10,Fcompleted this year and police say
OL,11,Fthey are just as committed to
OL,12,Finvestigate the tragedy as they were
OL,13,Fwhen it first happened.
OL,15,FDeputy Chief Constable Ben Snuggs
OL,16,Fsaid: "On the 10th anniversary of the
OL,17,Ftragic Didcot Power Station partial
OL,18,Fcollapse, our thoughts are firmly with
OL,19,FMichael, Ken, Christopher and John's
OL,20,Ffamily and friends.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,F"We are as committed today as we were
OL,8,Fon 23 February 2016 to diligently and
OL,9,Frigorously investigating this tragedy,
OL,10,Fwhich is shown through our
OL,11,Funprecedented work alongside our
OL,12,Fpartners over the last 10 years.
OL,14,F"We remain confident our investigation
OL,15,Ffor this complex case will be
OL,16,Ffinalised this year, as we said last
OL,17,Fmonth, to ensure the families get the
OL,18,Fanswers they deserve."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
