OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FThe Cresswell family said in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "As we mark ten years since
OL,9,Fthe Didcot Power Station collapse that
OL,10,Ftook the life of our beloved Dad,
OL,11,FGrandad, and Husband, Ken Cresswell,
OL,12,Fthe pain remains as deep and as raw as
OL,13,Fit was on 23 February 2016. The
OL,14,Firreplaceable void left in our lives
OL,15,Fis something we carry every single day.
OL,26,@pD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,F"Together, as a family, we stand
OL,8,Fstrong in our ongoing fight for
OL,9,Fjustice. We fully support Thames
OL,10,FValley Police, the Health and Safety
OL,11,FExecutive, and the Crown Prosecution
OL,12,FService as the investigation enters
OL,13,Fits final stages.
OL,15,F"After a decade of heartache and
OL,16,Fwaiting, we can only hope that the
OL,17,Fright thing is done and that justice
OL,18,Fis finally achieved for all the men
OL,19,Fwho never came home.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,F"Nobody should go to work and lose
OL,8,Ftheir life. Nobody should go to work
OL,9,Fin the morning and not return.
OL,11,F"Our love for our cherished Dad,
OL,12,FHusband, and Grandad remains as strong
OL,13,Fas ever, inspiring us to continue
OL,14,Fseeking the answers our family has
OL,15,Fwaited so long to hear.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,F"He is missed beyond words`every day,
OL,8,Fevery hour, in every part of our
OL,9,Flives. His memory guides us,
OL,10,Fstrengthens us, and reminds us why
OL,11,Fthis fight for answers and
OL,12,Faccountability matters so deeply.
OL,14,F"We will continue to stand together,
OL,15,Fdriven by love, determination, and the
OL,16,Fhope that justice will prevail."
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
