OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FIn a statement the Collings family
OL,8,Fsaid: "Ten years have passed since you
OL,9,Fleft us, and somehow the world has
OL,10,Fkept moving, even when it felt
OL,11,Fimpossible. Time will never erase you.
OL,13,F"Your laughter and your smile taught
OL,14,Fus that joy matters, that life is
OL,15,Fthere to be lived, and that a good
OL,16,Flaugh can carry us through the hardest
OL,17,Fmoments.
OL,19,F"We miss your smile. We miss your
OL,20,Flaugh. And we carry them with us,
OL,21,Falways.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,F"Forever loved. Forever remembered."
OL,9,FSandra Huxtable, Christopher's mother,
OL,10,Fsaid in a statement: "This has been
OL,11,Fthe hardest ten years of my life.
OL,13,F"No mother expects to lose a child.
OL,14,FFinally we will get justice so
OL,15,FChristopher can rest in peace with his
OL,16,Fbrother Jonathan. I wish to thank
OL,17,FThames Valley Police for all their
OL,18,Fsupport."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@dO]rD@VOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FTia Huxtable, Christopher's daughter,
OL,8,Fsaid in a statement: To be sitting
OL,9,Fhere at 21, when I was just 11 years
OL,10,Fold on 23rd February 2016, feels
OL,11,Funreal.
OL,13,F"It feels like forever since the day I
OL,14,Flost a huge part of me - my amazing
OL,15,Fdad. Ten years on, and there is still
OL,16,Fno justice for our men. But I truly
OL,17,Fbelieve the day will come when justice
OL,18,Fis finally served ` for our men, for
OL,19,Fus families, and for every family
OL,20,Faffected by that devastating day.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,F"We must continue to raise awareness
OL,8,Fworldwide so that a disaster like this
OL,9,Fnever happens again.
OL,11,F"I understand now that the length of
OL,12,Ftime we've waited for answers feels
OL,13,Fendless. For a long time, it was hard
OL,14,Fto understand why it has taken so long.
OL,16,F"But as I've grown, I can see that the
OL,17,Ftime taken is about making sure the
OL,18,Foutcome is the right one ` the best
OL,19,Fand fairest one possible.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,F"Ten years later, we have never given
OL,8,Fup on justice, and we never will until
OL,9,Fthe day it is served.
OL,11,F"Losing my dad at such a young age has
OL,12,Fhad a massive impact on my life. A
OL,13,Fwhole decade without him here with me
OL,14,Fand my mum - We miss him endlessly.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,F"He's not going to walk me down the
OL,8,Faisle. He's not going to meet his
OL,9,Ffuture grandchildren or see the life I
OL,10,Fbuild. Those are moments that will
OL,11,Falways feel incomplete without
OL,12,Fhim."But as long as I continue to make
OL,13,Fmy dad proud, I know I'll be okay.
OL,15,F"He will never be forgotten. And he
OL,16,Fwill most certainly never walk alone.
OL,17,FUntil the very end."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@EOUwD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771883476
OL,3,C'A living hell' Families reflect on
OL,4,C10th anniversary of power station
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FKirsty Shaw, John's daughter, said in
OL,8,Fa statement: "Ten years ago today, our
OL,9,Fhard-working, loving dad and husband
OL,10,Fwent to work and never returned home.
OL,12,F"Ten years have passed, and yet we
OL,13,Fstill have no answers as to why what
OL,14,Fhappened, happened.
OL,16,F"Time may go on for everyone else;
OL,17,Fhowever, my family and I still
OL,18,Fremember every single moment from that
OL,19,Fday - from the power station collapse
OL,20,Fup to the moment he was found and laid
OL,21,Fto rest.
OL,26,@pD@NOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
